{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^)()) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The block executed after the animation finishes."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation and completion"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"handler.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinat